title: S12 Ep146: Ed and Lorraine Warren: A Paranormal Love Story
itunes:title: Ed and Lorraine Warren: A Paranormal Love Story
description:
Wayback Week continues as we visit with legendary paranormal investigator Lorraine Warren! In the first part of the program, Lorraine talks about how she and Ed first met and fell in love, then fell into the paranormal together. In the second half of the program, Lorraine details some of their cases you have heard of, and some that you have never heard of before!
